node.text:
#GIVEAWAY! We’re teaming up with our friends from @yamazakihome to present a $250 gift card to one lucky winner. Visit the bio link of @yamazakihome to enter. This giveaway will be live until (08/01/2021, midnight EST).

Yamazaki Home is a Japanese housewares brand that marries style and function in their wide array of home furniture and organizers. They value simplicity and quality, as well as making your organization dreams a reality.
